value: Breeds from Kotzebue Sound, northern Mackenzie, northern Manitoba and Ungava, south to northern British Columbia, central Alberta and southern Manitoba; formerly to Illinois and New York. Winters in Chile and Argentina south to the Straits of Magellan, casually farther north; migrates chiefly east of the Rocky Mountains over the West Indies, Mexico and Central America.
